__property DictionaryElementCollection* XmlReader::get_Namespaces (   ) 
 

Returns all of the XML namespace declarations that are currently in-scope for the current position in the XML document being read.

Returns:
Returns GisDictionary. The dictionary has one GisDictionaryElement entry per namespace declaration. GisDictionaryElement->GetName() returns the namespace prefix. GisDictionaryElement->GetValue() returns the URI.
